# .dockerignore — keeps host secrets and dev cruft OUT of the built image.
#
# WHY THIS FILE MATTERS
# The Dockerfile does `COPY config/ ./config/`, `COPY user_files/ ./user_files/`
# and `COPY memory/ ./memory/` wholesale. Without exclusions, a real
# config/secrets.yaml, config/settings.yaml (HA token + relay secret) and the
# populated user_files/*.db (auth.db with password hashes) would be BAKED INTO
# every image layer — readable by anyone who `docker save`s or pulls the image.
# The canary suite (scripts/canary-validate.sh :: check_image_no_secrets)
# asserts these are absent from `docker save` output.
#
# RULE: exclude real/live config + user state, KEEP *.example / *.template files
# (the app + docs reference them) and KEEP tracked runtime skeletons the code
# loads by path (memory/*.json, routines/, utils/).
#
# At runtime the prod compose bind-mounts ./config and ./user_files back in, so
# excluding them from the image changes nothing operationally — it only stops
# the leak.

# ── Original entries (preserved) ──────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules
frontend/node_modules
frontend/dist
.git
.env
*.pyc
__pycache__
.venv
venv
*.log

# ── Secrets & live config (NEVER in an image) ─────────────────────────────────
config/secrets.yaml
config/settings.yaml
config/contacts.yaml
config/persons.json
config/audio_devices.yaml
docker/ha-config/secrets.yaml

# ── Live user state (DBs, generated JSON) ─────────────────────────────────────
user_files/*.db
user_files/*.db-shm
user_files/*.db-wal
user_files/*.json

# Hub runtime key material must never be near the build context.
etc-ziggy/
**/data_key
**/b2_credentials
kit_manifest.yaml

# ── Keep the templates / skeletons the broad excludes above would remove ──────
!config/settings.example.yaml
!config/settings.dev.yaml.example
!config/ziggy_memory.yaml
!config/.gitkeep
!user_files/.gitkeep

# ── Dev HA state / other stacks' data (huge, not needed to run Ziggy) ─────────
docker/ha-config-dev/
docker/z2m-data/
docker/z2m-data.example/
docker/mosquitto/passwordfile

# ── VCS / tooling / OS cruft ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
.gitignore
.github/
.claude/
.superpowers/
.playwright-mcp/
.tmp-screenshots/
**/.DS_Store
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
*.egg-info/

# ── Tests, docs, scratch, screenshots (not runtime deps) ──────────────────────
tests/
docs/
cache/
logs/
*.png
*.jpeg
*.jpg
ziggy-website/
ziggy_website/
